deMorgan

protected static Expression deMorgan(Negation negated)
Apply de Morgan's theorem:
  • NOT(a AND b) -> NOT(a) OR NOT(b)
  • NOT(a OR b) -> NOT(a) AND NOT(b)
Recursively does so till the NOT's are at the leaves
